snippet.title: Fantastyc Murder Mystery - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in a thrilling Murder Mystery where you play as the perpetrator or detective. Other players worldwide will scrutinize your every move as they attempt to solve your murders. Meanwhile, sift through evidence, and uncover the true culprit in unique player-generated crime scenes.

Wishlist the demo on Steam!
